### Accessibility

<Callout type="info" title="Keyboard & ARIA">
`Chat.Input` supports **Enter** to send and **Shift+Enter** for new lines. `Chat.SendButton` and `Chat.StopButton` are native `<button>` elements with `aria-label` attributes. The message list uses `role="log"` so screen readers announce new messages automatically.
</Callout>

