### What you'll build

A pair of dropdown selectors that let the user pick from available AI providers and models. The chat component stays blocked until a provider is selected.

<Callout type="info" title="Providers come from the vault">
  When you call `listProviders()`, the extension reads from the encrypted vault
  on the bridge. Adding and removing providers happens through the extension
  popup, which writes to the vault. The SDK never has direct access to
  credentials — it only sees provider names and available models.
</Callout>

