Add real-time streaming to see AI responses as they're generated.

### What you'll build

A chat interface that shows AI responses word-by-word as they arrive, with a streaming indicator and the ability to stop generation mid-stream.

<Callout type="info" title="Prerequisites">
  This tutorial builds on the [First Chat App](/docs/tutorials/first-chat-app)
  tutorial. Complete that first if you haven't already.
</Callout>

<StepList
  steps={[
    {
